name: ca-cam_Cam_CB_2018_spatial
annotation:
This is the model due to [Hi & al, 2018], Imlemented by Hi on smoldyn language and translated  to BNGL

Simple ligand-receptor binding model expressed in cell units:
*  time - seconds
*  concentration - M and molecule number (#)
*  volume - l
*  kinetic rates - M^(1-n)*s^-1 (n - order of reaction) and s^-1 (for #)
